description: While most guys can't stand their stepdads, Michael has what seems to be the stepdad of the year. Stepdad Jesse is a man's man, and Michael is just the man to take care of his stepdad's every need. When mom is away, stepdad Jesse knows how to take care of his stepsons' ass and shows the young man how to take care of daddy's cock. Everybody wants Michael's stepdad Jesse, but lucky Michael gets him first.
title: Stepdad of the Year
